00:33.000 --> 00:34.411
<i>His ring...</i>

00:35.636 --> 00:37.843
<i>I spent hours picking it out.</i>

00:39.073 --> 00:40.484
<i>Not knowing...</i>

00:41.909 --> 00:44.788
<i>I tried to ignore the signs, but...</i>

00:44.878 --> 00:47.017
<i>I could smell her on his clothes.</i>

00:48.682 --> 00:51.060
<i>Taste her on his lips.</i>

00:51.151 --> 00:53.461
<i>He confessed. He cried.</i>

00:53.554 --> 00:55.693
<i>I told him I forgave him, but...</i>

00:56.890 --> 00:58.267
<i>I didn't.</i>

00:59.460 --> 01:00.837
<i>I was broken.</i>

01:02.362 --> 01:04.137
<i>But I guess...</i>

01:04.230 --> 01:07.110
<i>none of us are perfect.</i>

01:10.471 --> 01:13.384
This is the hottest place in town.

01:14.908 --> 01:16.546
Really?

01:20.080 --> 01:22.560
This place is all kinds of wrong.

01:24.885 --> 01:26.455
Yeah, exactly, and it's perfect for you.

01:44.705 --> 01:45.683
Come on.

01:55.816 --> 01:57.124
You should go talk to him.

01:57.217 --> 01:59.219
I can talk to those boys any time.

01:59.319 --> 02:00.889
This is our weekend.

02:00.988 --> 02:03.366
You're right. We stick together.

02:03.457 --> 02:05.232
You ladies need a round?

02:05.926 --> 02:08.137
Not from you, Red. Thanks.

02:08.228 --> 02:10.071
I'll get us cocktails.

02:10.163 --> 02:13.475
No, I'll do it.

02:17.437 --> 02:20.043
That waitress looked
just like the home-wrecker.

02:25.412 --> 02:27.323
What are you looking for?

02:28.682 --> 02:30.958
Something to make me forget.

02:31.752 --> 02:33.390
If it were only that easy.

02:38.425 --> 02:40.405
You're staring.

02:42.663 --> 02:44.301
I'm sorry.

02:44.398 --> 02:46.537
You remind me of someone.

02:46.633 --> 02:48.544
I hope it's not a bad memory.

02:51.738 --> 02:53.046
She was...

02:54.741 --> 02:57.017
very special to me.

03:04.318 --> 03:05.729
Thank you.

03:10.257 --> 03:11.395
It's good.

03:11.491 --> 03:13.937
Hey, barman,
can I talk to you for a minute?

03:14.027 --> 03:15.199
My name's Patrick.

03:15.295 --> 03:16.501
Tara.

03:16.597 --> 03:17.598
Tara.

03:17.698 --> 03:18.972
Hey, buddy?

03:19.066 --> 03:20.977
Can I talk to you?

03:21.068 --> 03:23.105
You should probably
go take care of that guy.

03:23.971 --> 03:26.474
I don't want to look away.

03:26.573 --> 03:27.847
Why not?

03:27.941 --> 03:29.579
You might disappear.

03:32.212 --> 03:33.384
Nice ink.

03:35.182 --> 03:37.492
Christ, man, get over here!

03:37.584 --> 03:39.393
I'll be right back.

03:43.624 --> 03:45.035
Hey, what the fuck is this?

03:45.125 --> 03:47.571
I'm not paying $40 for two fucking drinks.

03:48.362 --> 03:50.672
You don't have to drink it.

03:50.764 --> 03:52.903
- You can leave.
- I'm gonna kick your ass.

04:01.441 --> 04:02.579
Let's go.

04:09.616 --> 04:11.653
What did you say to that guy?

04:11.752 --> 04:13.060
Nothing.

04:17.156 --> 04:18.659
I sent you all a round.

04:22.629 --> 04:23.699
Thank you.

04:24.765 --> 04:26.506
What do I owe you?

04:26.600 --> 04:27.601
It's on me.

04:48.188 --> 04:49.531
That was so cool!

04:49.623 --> 04:52.194
Where do we get a car?

04:52.292 --> 04:54.033
I gotta go.

04:54.127 --> 04:57.836
Hey, that bartender
you were talking to earlier.

04:57.931 --> 04:59.911
He's standing over there.

05:02.736 --> 05:04.238
He's so hot.

05:04.338 --> 05:06.147
He's so cute. You should go talk to him.

05:06.239 --> 05:08.014
- Shut up.
- You were already talking to him!

05:08.108 --> 05:09.280
I'm not going to talk to him.

05:09.376 --> 05:11.447
- You were flirting with him.
- You totally were.

05:11.545 --> 05:13.354
Speak louder, that would be great.

05:13.447 --> 05:15.358
- Just talk to him.
- I hate you.

05:17.884 --> 05:18.954
Hi.

05:22.622 --> 05:24.101
You again.

05:25.625 --> 05:27.298
Me again.

05:45.178 --> 05:46.589
I should be going.

05:58.792 --> 06:00.100
Thank you.

06:03.964 --> 06:05.272
Good night.

06:09.369 --> 06:11.007
Shut up. So what?

06:30.757 --> 06:33.135
Who keeps calling?

06:33.226 --> 06:34.227
Man...

06:37.364 --> 06:38.968
No one.

06:39.065 --> 06:41.375
All right, ladies,
it's time for Bloody Marys.

08:08.421 --> 08:09.399
I can't.

10:39.239 --> 10:41.048
You're awake.

10:45.278 --> 10:46.518
Where are my clothes?

10:47.781 --> 10:49.658
They smelled like a club.

10:49.749 --> 10:51.456
I washed them for you.

10:54.654 --> 10:56.634
You washed my clothes?

10:56.723 --> 10:58.259
When?

10:58.358 --> 11:01.168
Couldn't sleep, really.

11:01.261 --> 11:03.070
Don't worry, I handwashed your dress.

11:04.464 --> 11:06.171
They're in the bathroom.

11:11.271 --> 11:12.978
Would you like some coffee?

11:13.073 --> 11:14.711
I brewed some.

11:14.808 --> 11:16.651
Yeah, sure.

11:19.446 --> 11:21.983
Do you have a T-shirt or something?

11:22.082 --> 11:23.561
Yeah, in the wardrobe.

11:24.784 --> 11:26.229
What's mine is yours.

11:39.966 --> 11:41.604
You take sugar and cream?

11:42.769 --> 11:44.874
You know, I...

11:44.971 --> 11:47.508
I'm probably gonna skip
the coffee, actually.

11:52.545 --> 11:54.218
Do you wanna grab breakfast?

11:55.982 --> 11:58.258
I know a place that serves great crepes.

11:58.351 --> 11:59.989
Best in New Orleans.

12:08.728 --> 12:10.036
So?

12:11.931 --> 12:13.706
I have to get going.

12:15.535 --> 12:17.412
- So soon?
- Yeah.

12:20.039 --> 12:22.019
Well, wait. I want to show you something.

12:24.944 --> 12:26.116
You know, I have to catch a flight.

12:26.212 --> 12:28.214
- I'm sorry, I can't.
- It's important.

12:30.483 --> 12:33.020
Okay. What is it?

12:38.324 --> 12:41.237
I meet a lot of girls, and...
but you, you're...

12:45.732 --> 12:47.268
From the moment I met you...

12:49.936 --> 12:51.711
I knew you'd come back for me.

12:54.574 --> 12:56.383
Come back?

12:56.476 --> 12:57.853
Yeah.

13:04.184 --> 13:06.357
You're the one who can save me.

13:10.123 --> 13:11.966
You don't like it?

13:12.058 --> 13:13.867
I did it for you.

13:13.960 --> 13:16.304
I'm sorry. This was a mistake.

13:16.396 --> 13:18.137
Don't say that. We have something special.

13:18.231 --> 13:20.609
No, I... I really should have never come.

13:21.868 --> 13:23.575
Don't leave.

13:26.272 --> 13:28.718
You know, I...

13:28.808 --> 13:30.810
I've got to catch my flight.

13:30.910 --> 13:33.618
Why? Stay.

13:39.519 --> 13:41.430
I can't.

13:44.724 --> 13:45.964
I really have to go.

13:46.059 --> 13:48.039
- It's just...
- It's okay.

13:52.599 --> 13:54.408
I need to go now.

14:22.195 --> 14:24.607
Oh, my God. You do realize
our plane leaves in an hour.

14:24.697 --> 14:26.472
Yes, I know.

14:26.566 --> 14:28.170
What the hell happened to you last night?

14:28.268 --> 14:30.475
I fucked up. I don't want to talk
about it right now.

14:32.305 --> 14:33.443
Where's Justine?

14:33.539 --> 14:34.916
She left already.

14:39.512 --> 14:41.423
I can't find my phone.

14:41.514 --> 14:43.323
- Here, I'll call it.
- Thanks.

15:04.103 --> 15:05.810
I don't hear it anywhere.

15:07.106 --> 15:08.983
Shit. My whole life is in that thing, man.

15:09.075 --> 15:11.419
Well, it's too bad.
You're gonna have to buy a new one.

15:13.179 --> 15:14.817
Let's just go, I gotta get out of here.

15:36.869 --> 15:38.246
Hi.

15:38.338 --> 15:39.874
Welcome home, sweetheart.

15:39.973 --> 15:41.646
You're the best.

15:41.741 --> 15:44.813
So, how was the bachelorette weekend?

15:44.911 --> 15:46.788
You know, we did a bunch of girly stuff.

15:46.879 --> 15:48.950
You would have hated it.

15:49.048 --> 15:50.391
You're such a gentleman.

15:50.483 --> 15:51.587
He is.

15:51.684 --> 15:53.493
Look. It's a picture of your sister.

15:53.586 --> 15:55.930
I told you those dresses were gonna look
great on everyone.

15:57.890 --> 15:59.460
Don't say anything.

15:59.559 --> 16:01.266
Don't say anything. It's not worth it.

16:02.762 --> 16:04.867
What are we whispering about?

16:04.964 --> 16:07.308
Well, if we told you,
it wouldn't be a secret.

16:07.400 --> 16:08.606
- I gotta go.
- Bye.

16:08.701 --> 16:10.510
Bye, sweetheart.

16:10.603 --> 16:12.207
- Debra.
- Bye.

16:13.840 --> 16:15.342
- Hi.
- Hi.

16:18.244 --> 16:19.587
So, I'm...

16:19.679 --> 16:23.486
I'm not gonna really be seeing very much
of you these next couple of weeks, am I?

16:23.583 --> 16:25.961
I just need to finish planning everything.

16:26.052 --> 16:26.996
Okay.

16:29.122 --> 16:31.193
I just want one last night.

16:33.126 --> 16:34.571
What's up with your phone?

16:34.660 --> 16:36.105
I've been trying to call.

17:01.187 --> 17:03.064
So, how we doing today?

17:09.262 --> 17:10.468
Well...

17:14.467 --> 17:16.571
I couldn't be better.

17:16.669 --> 17:17.977
I'm in love.

17:18.971 --> 17:20.176
That's great.

17:26.145 --> 17:28.125
She's an angel.

17:29.782 --> 17:31.819
Definitely not this.

17:31.918 --> 17:33.761
- Not this...
- Okay.

17:33.853 --> 17:35.628
You know, I like this for sure.

17:35.721 --> 17:37.496
Okay.

17:37.590 --> 17:38.864
This one, I'm not so sure about.

17:38.958 --> 17:40.164
- Okay.
- I'm sorry, one sec.

17:40.259 --> 17:41.829
Sure.

17:41.928 --> 17:44.238
Excuse me. Hey, babe.

17:44.330 --> 17:47.937
Just wanted to let you know
that I picked up my tux,

17:48.034 --> 17:49.707
and I'm officially done.

17:49.802 --> 17:51.372
<i>I hate you.</i>

17:51.471 --> 17:54.213
Wait. Does that mean
that the wedding is off?

17:54.307 --> 17:55.513
That's such a bummer.

17:55.608 --> 17:57.679
I am so swamped right now.

17:57.777 --> 17:59.347
I have so much more to do.

17:59.445 --> 18:01.356
You know what, babe,
can I call you back in a few?

18:01.447 --> 18:02.448
<i>No, wait.</i>

18:02.548 --> 18:04.528
I want to see you tonight.

18:04.617 --> 18:06.528
Alone.

18:06.619 --> 18:07.791
<i>I don't know, Michael.</i>

18:07.887 --> 18:09.457
<i>I have so many plans to get done.</i>

18:09.555 --> 18:10.499
- <i>And I'm just...</i>
- Babe?

18:10.590 --> 18:11.830
- <i>I'm feeling...</i>
- Babe.

18:11.924 --> 18:13.301
You need to relax, all right?

18:13.392 --> 18:16.066
It's just... just one night.

18:19.031 --> 18:20.704
Okay. When and where?

18:21.934 --> 18:22.912
Where, when?

18:23.002 --> 18:26.976
I'll be at your place at 6:00,
unless I can get out of the hotel earlier.

18:27.073 --> 18:29.053
Okay, it's a date.

19:07.480 --> 19:09.482
I got caught up in the moment, but...

21:35.861 --> 21:37.340
I've missed this.

21:37.430 --> 21:38.738
Me, too.

21:40.032 --> 21:43.206
- What's wrong?
- What are you doing here?

21:43.302 --> 21:45.543
- No, get out!
- Just calm down.

21:45.638 --> 21:48.551
If you don't get out of here right now,
I am calling the cops.

21:48.641 --> 21:51.121
- No...
- Whoa. Hey. Hey!

21:55.948 --> 21:57.120
Oh, my God.

21:57.216 --> 22:00.823
Hey, listen. I just wanted to see you.

22:04.690 --> 22:05.964
That's all.

22:09.929 --> 22:12.000
How did you find me?

22:14.533 --> 22:16.137
You left your phone.

22:22.775 --> 22:24.516
All right, I get it.

22:26.879 --> 22:29.553
I understand. You're surprised to see me.

22:30.850 --> 22:32.921
Maybe if you give me
a chance to talk about it...

22:33.018 --> 22:34.258
No. No.

22:34.353 --> 22:36.128
I have nothing to say to you.

22:37.990 --> 22:39.901
Michael's gonna be here any minute.

22:41.727 --> 22:42.933
Michael?

22:45.364 --> 22:47.537
Michael, your fiancé?

22:52.738 --> 22:55.275
You haven't told him
about us yet, have you?

22:59.612 --> 23:01.523
You know what? Look, I'm...

23:03.115 --> 23:05.823
I'm sorry if I misled you.

23:07.086 --> 23:09.623
But I want to make this perfectly clear.

23:11.190 --> 23:13.670
There is nothing between us.

23:17.263 --> 23:18.742
You don't believe that.

23:23.669 --> 23:25.239
I love you.

23:26.739 --> 23:29.049
I don't understand why
you can't do me the courtesy...

23:30.142 --> 23:31.951
of just talking with me.

23:33.846 --> 23:37.589
Maybe if you open up,
then maybe you'll see...

23:38.951 --> 23:40.055
Shit!

23:40.152 --> 23:41.722
You have to get out of here right now!

23:41.821 --> 23:43.596
- Get out!
- Not out.

23:43.689 --> 23:45.430
Not until you talk to me.

23:48.127 --> 23:49.834
- You say you love me?
- Yes.

23:49.929 --> 23:51.101
And you don't want to hurt me?

23:51.197 --> 23:52.175
Of course not.

23:52.264 --> 23:55.245
Then I need you to leave right now.

23:55.334 --> 23:56.836
- Please.
- I won't go anywhere

23:56.936 --> 23:58.779
until you tell me you'll meet me.

23:58.871 --> 24:01.681
- Okay, yes, I'll meet you.
- Where?

24:04.243 --> 24:07.247
There's a coffee shop on Lincoln,
just south of Pico.

24:07.346 --> 24:10.624
I can meet you there at 10:00 tomorrow,
but only if you leave now.

24:10.716 --> 24:12.718
- Please.
- Ten.

24:12.818 --> 24:14.024
Yes.

24:18.858 --> 24:20.269
Babe?

24:24.430 --> 24:25.875
You all right?

24:25.965 --> 24:27.410
Yeah.

24:27.500 --> 24:28.979
Yeah, I was...

24:29.068 --> 24:31.207
I was about to get in the shower,

24:31.303 --> 24:33.340
and I thought I heard a noise.

24:33.439 --> 24:35.385
Noise?

24:35.474 --> 24:37.977
What was the noise?

24:38.077 --> 24:40.455
It was nothing.

24:40.546 --> 24:41.820
Okay.

24:43.182 --> 24:46.856
All right, well, why don't you go get ready,
because we have an earlier reservation.

24:46.952 --> 24:48.329
Okay.

24:50.222 --> 24:52.133
Are you sure you're okay?

24:52.224 --> 24:54.067
Yeah. Yes.

24:55.661 --> 24:57.140
I'll go get dressed.

24:57.229 --> 24:58.299
Okay.

25:19.118 --> 25:23.631
So, everything's booked, set up
at the hotel for all the wedding guests.

25:25.457 --> 25:28.131
You know, I was also thinking that...

25:31.730 --> 25:32.868
Hey?

25:32.965 --> 25:34.137
What?

25:36.702 --> 25:39.774
I can't help but feel like
I'm dining alone here.

25:43.809 --> 25:46.255
I'm sorry.

25:46.345 --> 25:49.383
I've just been really overwhelmed lately.

25:58.691 --> 26:01.171
You know, it was...

26:01.260 --> 26:04.639
only a one-time thing, right?

26:04.730 --> 26:07.677
I hate that you found her card
before I could tell you.

26:07.766 --> 26:09.268
It almost ruined us.

26:12.705 --> 26:16.118
Every single day,

26:16.208 --> 26:17.744
I am thankful for...

26:19.511 --> 26:21.616
I mean, you gave me a second chance.

26:23.082 --> 26:27.720
If you're having second thoughts
or doubts, just tell me.

26:27.820 --> 26:29.424
No.

26:29.521 --> 26:31.501
No, absolutely not.

26:32.858 --> 26:36.396
There is no one in this world
that I love more than you.

26:36.495 --> 26:38.998
And I'm so sorry

26:39.098 --> 26:42.238
if I've been distracted this past week.

26:43.268 --> 26:44.508
It's not you.

26:46.438 --> 26:48.418
It's the wedding.

26:48.507 --> 26:51.784
I mean, I don't know
how people go through this process

26:51.877 --> 26:54.118
and still stay together, but...

26:56.248 --> 26:58.125
I love you.

26:58.217 --> 26:59.753
And I'm excited.

27:01.053 --> 27:02.862
I love you.

28:09.722 --> 28:12.259
All right, rise and shine.

28:12.357 --> 28:14.428
You can't sleep the day away, babe.

28:17.062 --> 28:18.564
So, you're gonna be like that, are you?

28:19.898 --> 28:21.673
Are you all right?

28:21.767 --> 28:23.747
Yeah.

28:23.836 --> 28:26.077
I just... I had a bad dream.

28:26.171 --> 28:27.411
Okay.

28:31.110 --> 28:33.750
You expecting someone this early?

28:33.846 --> 28:35.154
No.

28:36.749 --> 28:40.196
No. You just go get dressed,
and I'll get the door.

28:45.524 --> 28:47.868
Well, whoever it is,
they are awfully persistent.

28:49.795 --> 28:51.832
All right, I'm coming.

28:56.602 --> 28:57.876
Hello, Debra.

28:57.970 --> 29:00.280
Hey. Tara! Tara!

29:00.372 --> 29:02.249
Please, come on in.

29:03.976 --> 29:05.216
Tara.

29:05.310 --> 29:07.312
Hey, come on, girl, get dressed.
We gotta go.

29:07.412 --> 29:08.686
What are you talking about?

29:08.781 --> 29:10.351
Our spa day, remember?

29:10.449 --> 29:11.860
- Shit.
- Yeah.

29:11.950 --> 29:14.055
No, I can't. I've got
an appointment this morning.

29:14.153 --> 29:15.598
With who?

29:15.687 --> 29:16.859
No one. I just, I have...

29:16.955 --> 29:19.458
Okay, well, you're gonna have to cancel.

29:19.558 --> 29:22.095
Well, that does not sound like
anything I want to be a part of,

29:22.194 --> 29:24.765
but have fun, love you.

29:24.863 --> 29:27.002
- Debra.
- Bye.

29:27.099 --> 29:28.976
What are you doing? Get dressed.

29:29.067 --> 29:31.809
All right, just...

29:31.904 --> 29:34.009
- Five minutes.
- Okay.

30:10.108 --> 30:11.519
You came.

30:12.611 --> 30:13.817
Of course I did.

30:16.648 --> 30:18.127
Before you say anything...

30:20.886 --> 30:23.628
I've thought a lot about what you said.

30:27.326 --> 30:28.703
And you're right.

30:30.963 --> 30:32.374
I'm right?

30:33.398 --> 30:35.378
We belong together.

30:39.905 --> 30:42.146
I want to hear you say something.

30:44.977 --> 30:46.388
Anything.

30:47.746 --> 30:49.919
Tell me you love me.

31:00.158 --> 31:02.604
With all my soul.

31:02.694 --> 31:05.072
More coffee?

31:05.163 --> 31:07.006
What?

31:07.099 --> 31:08.806
More coffee?

31:21.747 --> 31:24.284
Wait. Who were you supposed
to be meeting with this morning?

31:24.383 --> 31:26.420
I don't want to talk about it.

31:26.518 --> 31:27.758
Listen, I get it, girl.

31:27.853 --> 31:29.161
Weddings are really stressful.

31:29.254 --> 31:30.426
Do you want a Valium?

31:30.522 --> 31:32.559
No, no. It's not that.

31:34.626 --> 31:36.196
It's him.

31:36.295 --> 31:38.172
Who's him?

31:38.263 --> 31:39.833
Patrick.

31:39.932 --> 31:41.878
He showed up at my house.

31:44.202 --> 31:46.705
Wait. That guy you hooked up with
two weeks ago?

31:49.808 --> 31:52.652
Christ. And you were gonna meet with him?

31:52.744 --> 31:54.724
Yeah, to tell him to stay away.

31:54.813 --> 31:56.520
I can't have him showing up
at my house, Deb.

31:56.615 --> 31:57.958
No... Absolutely not.

31:58.050 --> 32:00.394
You don't go meet with him, okay?

32:00.485 --> 32:02.123
You have to cut him off completely.

