didn't exactly take it well.</i>

41:17.208 --> 41:18.414
Come on, Patrick!

41:18.510 --> 41:20.820
Get out! Patrick, get out!

41:20.912 --> 41:22.550
Go!

41:22.647 --> 41:27.588
