died a few days later from the burns.

41:28.753 --> 41:30.357
Jesus.

41:30.455 --> 41:33.129
I'd say he has a type, wouldn't you?

41:35.093 --> 41:38.506
He's got a half-dozen
restraining orders against him.

41:38.596 --> 41:40.473
