43:04.349 --> 43:05.589
Okay.

44:44.816 --> 44:47.729
Whoa... I'm sorry.

44:47.819 --> 44:49.196
- Sorry.
- I'm sorry.

44:49.287 --> 44:50.994
- I didn't see you there.
- Yeah.

44:51.089 --> 44:52.227
Are you okay? I'm sorry.

44:52.323 --> 44:54.462
