45:42.473 --> 45:44.475
He's a beauty.

45:44.575 --> 45:45.747
Is he yours?

45:45.843 --> 45:47.254
Yeah.

45:49.280 --> 45:51.556
You think I could...

45:51.649 --> 45:53.026
take a picture?

45:53.117 --> 45:54.357
Sure, I guess.

45:54.452 --> 45:56.227
- Both of you?
- Yeah.

46:01.993 --> 46:03.063
Good.

46:03.161 --> 46:04.469
Perfect.

46:08.833 --> 46:09.937
I'm Patrick.

46:10.034 --> 46:11.308
