46:30.188 --> 46:31.531
They don't ride though.

46:32.890 --> 46:34.392
Tara...

46:35.526 --> 46:37.597
that's a...

46:37.695 --> 46:39.265
That's a beautiful name.

46:40.331 --> 46:41.605
I know a Tara.

46:41.699 --> 46:44.407
What's she like?

46:44.502 --> 46:47.711
