50:35.499 --> 50:36.705
Who is that?

50:36.801 --> 50:38.075
I met him at the stables.

50:38.169 --> 50:40.115
- He's sexy.
- I know, right?

50:42.440 --> 50:45.319
Will you make sure their luggage makes it
to the rooftop suite, please?

50:45.409 --> 50:47.411
Oh, my God! The rooftop suite?

50:47.511 --> 50:48.785
This place is awesome.

50:48.879 --> 50:51.689
I am totally going to live
in a place like this...

50:53.084 --> 50:55.621
Where is my eldest?

50:55.719 --> 50:57.062
Has Tara gotten here yet?

50:57.154 --> 50:58.462
