50:58.556 --> 51:00.126
Michael?

51:01.592 --> 51:03.594
It's nice to finally meet you.

51:03.694 --> 51:07.437
I'm sorry. I'm afraid
you have me at a disadvantage.

51:07.531 --> 51:10.671
Patrick. Patrick Flynn.

51:10.768 --> 51:13.009
- Right.
- Tara hasn't mentioned me?

51:13.104 --> 51:14.742
Michael, would you mind if we head up?

51:14.839 --> 51:17.410
Sure. Let's make sure they get
to their room and everything's good.

51:17.508 --> 51:18.543
- Great, thanks.
- All right.

51:18.642 --> 51:20.121
I'll see you guys in a little bit.
One second.

51:20.211 --> 51:21.349
Thank you.

51:24.281 --> 51:27.888
