52:16.467 --> 52:18.469
before my wedding.

52:18.569 --> 52:20.606
- Nothing?
- Nothing.

52:20.704 --> 52:23.150
Nothing is going to upset you.

52:23.240 --> 52:24.742
Nothing.

52:27.478 --> 52:29.287
Well, you should ask Tara about me.

52:29.380 --> 52:30.984
Fuck you.

52:31.081 --> 52:32.719
Michael!

52:37.221 --> 52:40.031
